__ Cantrip: Haunt ____________________________ Cost: 15 ______________________

Use:  cantrip haunt                            Material Component: none
Use:  C haunt

The cantrip haunt is a minor magic of the sphere of illusion.  Like its
sister cantrip groan, the cantrip haunt will generate illusionary sounds.
It will also generate various unnerving sights, which will be seen/heard 
in the immediate area for the next few minutes.  To dispel the cantrip,
say < haunt off >
